bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "sugondat-da-adapter"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.68"
async-trait = "0.1.71"
digest = "0.10.7"
parity-scale-codec = "3.6.3"
tracing = "0.1.37"

[dependencies.borsh]
version = "0.10.3"
features = ["bytes"]

[dependencies.bytes]
version = "1"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.hex]
version = "0.4.3"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.jsonrpsee]
version = "0.20.3"
features = ["ws-client"]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.sha2]
version = "0.10.6"
default-features = false

[dependencies.sov-rollup-interface]
git = "https://github.com/Sovereign-Labs/sovereign-sdk"
rev = "6058b31"

[dependencies.sugondat-nmt]
path = "../../sugondat-nmt"
default-features = false

[dependencies.sugondat-shim-common-sovereign]
path = "../../sugondat-shim/common/sovereign"
features = ["client"]
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
optional = true

[features]
default = ["native"]
native = ["sov-rollup-interface/native", "sugondat-nmt/serde", "sugondat-nmt/native", "dep:tokio", "dep:jsonrpsee", "dep:sugondat-shim-common-sovereign"]
verifier = ["sugondat-nmt/serde"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "sugondat_da_adapter"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]

bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "sugondat-node"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
